Generate new address using 
    node scripts/future_address.js

Upgrading Grotto
    Call Grotto.updateGrotto(newAddress) using old Grotto. 
    This call with update the addresses in Store and GrottoToken and send all unspent ETH to new Address

Upgrading Gov
    Call Governance.updateGov(newAddress) using old Gov.

You can enable these buttons in the GUI by setting isAdmin to true;

Store and GrottoToken updates will require Grotto and Governance updates too since Grotto and Governance don't store any data that can't be lost